snippet.title: Summoning Exodia against Rex Raptor - Yu-Gi-Oh! Worldwide Edition: Stairway to the Destined Duel
snippet.description:
Played a game against Rex Raptor with my Exodia Deck.Exodia is summoned at 4:38

Yu Gi Oh! Worldwide Edition: Stairway to the Destined Duel is an awesome game,bought it 9 years ago,now i play it again after so much time in VisualBoy Advance.I recommend playing it,although it has very old cards.
